messages.message: I chatted with a former coworker who is at Docker now — there is a big shakeup happening internally (driven by the CEO change a few weeks ago). Sounds like a lot of people are looking to get out, him included. Sounds like y’all have already noticed something going over there; but thought you might like the confirmation.
Yeah had dinner w Salesforce friend last night and he said the same: folks are trying to get out for fear of “new CEO with new agenda and all existing teams put through the blender”
I didn’t realize they announced ceo departure at their annual conference. What a buzzkill
